> [!TIP]
> To use the LeetCode API locally via Docker, run:
> `docker run -p 3001:3000 alfaarghya/alfa-leetcode-api:2.0.3`

> [!NOTE]
> Database columns were verified and the schema was reloaded. If you still see "column not found" errors, a quick restart of your local Supabase stack will force a full cache refresh.
